Title: East to west
DateModified: '2019-02-04'
DatePublished: '2019-02-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/east-to-west
SetInCountry: China
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Ev Jam
AuthorCountry: Guam
Text: Grew up in England, went to China to work ,took off bus through inner Mongolia,,
  hitchhiked to ulaanbator , buses russian trucks  and horse riding with locals to
  katgal lake, and happened to be there on their local nadaam, a celebration traditional
  wrestling and horse racing! Backpacked down through China with a friend, 3000+m
  sunrise mntain camp on one of the three Buddhist mntains, zhatong!! ended up in
  Vietnam , mopeding and camping in the rice paddies, Hanoi lock downs and beautiful
  catba island , amazing locals and help out stories as well as funny fails and randomness
  (..but saved for if I really write this ) :))
